  <h3>Manage Third-Party Scripts</h3>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Audit regularly</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Load with async/defer</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Self-host when possible</li>
  </ul>

  {# ── Key Takeaways ── #}
  <h2 id="key-takeaways" class="vf-u-margin--0 vf-u-padding__top--400 vf-u-padding__bottom--600">Key Takeaways</h2>

  <p><strong>JavaScript cost = network + processing + execution</strong></p>

  <p>Performance improves by:</p>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Code splitting</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Lazy loading</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Removing unused code</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Avoiding heavy frameworks</li>
  </ul>

  {# ── Do / Don't ── #}
  <h2 id="dos-dont" class="vf-u-margin--0 vf-u-padding__top--400 vf-u-padding__bottom--600 vf-search-client-side--no-index">Do / Don't</h2>

  <h4>Do</h4>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Use small modules</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Split code by feature</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Measure performance</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Remove unused JavaScript</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Don't</h4>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Ship large frameworks unnecessarily</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Include unused libraries</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Overuse third-party scripts</li>
  </ul>

  {# ── Checklist ── #}
  <h2 id="checklist" class="vf-u-margin--0 vf-u-padding__top--400 vf-u-padding__bottom--600">Checklist</h2>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Remove unused JavaScript</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Split code by feature</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Replace heavy libraries with native APIs</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Cache DOM lookups</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Use async loading</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Optimise loops and conditions</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Avoid inline script duplication</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Profile before and after changes</li>
  </ul>

  {# ── Metrics & tools ── #}
  <h2 id="metrics" class="vf-u-margin--0 vf-u-padding__top--400 vf-u-padding__bottom--600">Metrics &amp; tools</h2>
  
  <p>To ensure LRO compliance, continuously monitor:</p>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Bundle size (compressed JS)</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">JS execution time</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Time to Interactive (TTI)</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Total Blocking Time (TBT)</li>
  </ul>

  <p>These metrics reflect real user experience on constrained devices.</p>

